# Code Ownership Rules
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for all files
* @development-team

# Third-party modules - DevOps team ONLY
third_party_addons/ @devops-team
third_party_addons/** @devops-team

# Critical configuration files - Senior developers + DevOps
config/odoo.conf @senior-developers @devops-team
config/requirements.txt @senior-developers @devops-team

# Git configuration - DevOps only
.githooks/ @devops-team
.githooks/** @devops-team
CODEOWNERS @devops-team

# Scripts require review
scripts/ @senior-developers @devops-team
scripts/** @senior-developers @devops-team

# Documentation - anyone can contribute
*.md @development-team
docs/ @development-team
docs/** @development-team
